---
import "./CardDrivesWork2.css";
---

<article class="round no-elevate p-0 wave">
  <div class="gfx gfx-cycle" role="img" aria-label="Two markers traveling in opposite directions around a ring, suggesting a continuous exchange between practice and teaching">
    <div class="orbit">
      <span class="orbiter o1"></span>
      <span class="orbiter o2"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-5">
    <h3 class="text-3 lh-2 fw-6">The cycle of build and share</h3>
    <p class="text-1 mt-2">Real work produces real insight. We do not keep that insight to ourselves. It becomes the foundation of what we teach through Stackdemy, so the next generation of work is sharper for everyone.</p>
  </div>
</article>
